title: BNP. Paying The Price Of Uncontrolled Immigration. The Truth. .w
description: Witness the truth about Blairs failed multi-cultural Britain. An interview between Nick Cass, Clr. Angela Clarke and a white resident who has been on the receiving end of a campaign of racial harassment by young Muslim thugs. A distressing story which includes threat of eviction by the landlord, death threats and physical assaults. An everyday story of life for white folks in multi-cultural Britain.(from www.bnp.org.uk)
